      "role": "user",
      "content": "a migraine?? i dont know, it was way more sudden than my usual headaches. like it went from 0 to 100 in a split second. i'm also kinda feeling a little bit of nausea and my neck feels a bit stiff. u sure it's just dehydration? i'm kinda worried about going to the clinic since it's late and it'll be expensive if it's nothing. can i just take the ibuprofen and sleep it off?",
